⚙️ Architecture & Components
cli.py: Entry point handling user inputs, arguments, and command routing using click.

collector.py: Interacts with the Kubernetes Python Client to retrieve live objects (Pods, Nodes, Namespaces).

analyzer.py: The core logical engine evaluating fetched resources against custom-built health and security validation rules.

reporter.py: Formats the diagnostic results into high-quality terminal tables using rich.
